{"tid":1965415,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"谷歌fb海底光纜獲批 惟不能直連香港","createTime":"2020-04-09T12:42:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T12:42:01.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2a168d3bc092abda52e4353812e57489df9c0f19","tid":1965415,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:42:01.000Z","msg":"谷歌(Google)和Facebook(fb)的跨太平洋海底光纜建設計劃，獲得美國監管機構的批准，但前提是該光纜不能直接連接到香港。<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦通訊委員會(FCC)稱，假如海底光纜直連美國和香港，便存在着嚴重威脅美國國家安全的重大風險。<br />\n<br />\nFCC指出，只要光纜運營商同意這些保障措施，美國安全機構不會反對擬建中的海底光纜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2431978/%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8Cfb%E6%B5%B7%E5%BA%95%E5%85%89%E7%BA%9C%E7%8D%B2%E6%89%B9+%E6%83%9F%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E7%9B%B4%E9%80%A3%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2431978%2F%25E8%25B0%25B7%25E6%25AD%258Cfb%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25BA%2595%25E5%2585%2589%25E7%25BA%259C%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2589%25B9%2B%25E6%2583%259F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E7%259B%25B4%25E9%2580%25A3%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVa6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=da51ead5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2431978/%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8Cfb%E6%B5%B7%E5%BA%95%E5%85%89%E7%BA%9C%E7%8D%B2%E6%89%B9+%E6%83%9F%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E7%9B%B4%E9%80%A3%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF</a>"}]}